{"tid":2425302,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年少年股神既未來","createTime":"2021-02-27T09:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T09:41:42.000Z","uid":284376,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c823d8b1a4fc6f83170167ce85c48695597c08bd","tid":2425302,"uid":284376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"經歷完瘋牛後，由日日IG/公司不斷曬命賺幾十萬，少年股神第一次面對回調既決擇，由賺變蝕，到依家唔敢出聲同人講賺定蝕，面對風險，少年股神心入面有一句Stronghold，搏盡無悔，但每日面對跌市既壓力越黎越大，發現一日蝕既錢係一兩個月既人工，開始沒心機做野<br />\n<br />\n升，調整完繼續牛氣沖天，少年股神正式成為股神，係被選中既細路，IG日日開POST每日賺10幾20萬，買股票沒窮人，人人財務自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌，熊市正式開始，少年股神相信QE係唔會股災，繼續SH自命不凡，不斷溝貨，每日心驚膽跳等待下一輪牛市，結果股joy，慾哭無淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5dc04bc9a369d0c96a68839cf2689de0be50f1","tid":2425302,"uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"諗起彪大佬講美國無限QE個POST<br />\n股市有乜理由會跌<br />\n所以只會係牛市<br />\n上帝都推唔冧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510e4df4d9ca8e1d90e26b887462b7b29bb80326","tid":2425302,"uid":284376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd5dc04bc9a369d0c96a68839cf2689de0be50f1","tid":2425302,"uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"諗起彪大佬講美國無限QE個POST<br />\n股市有乜理由會跌<br />\n所以只會係牛市<br />\n上帝都推唔冧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"諗唔到股災理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b1a81514dab63f843bc759442d68beda2a9db0","tid":2425302,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T